name: GNU TeXmacs
description: GNU TeXmacs is an excellent scientific document publishing software. You can not only directly export to PDF by compiling, but also import and export to TeX and HTML files. Its full visual tables, formula editing environment and structured browsing function will bring you a true "WYSIWYG" experience.

en_US.description: GNU TeXmacs is an excellent scientific document publishing software. You can not only directly export to PDF by compiling, but also import and export to TeX and HTML files. Its full visual tables, formula editing environment and structured browsing function will bring you a true "WYSIWYG" experience.
en_US.name: GNU TeXmacs

zh_CN.description: GNU TeXmacs是一个优秀的科学文档排版软件，您可以不通过编译直接导出为PDF格式的文件，也可以导入和导出为TeX、HTML格式的文件。其完全可视化的表格和公式编辑环境、结构化的浏览功能，将带给您真正的“所见即所得”的体验。
zh_CN.name: GNU TeXmacs
